TASK STATUS UPDATES:
- When starting a task: set status to "in_progress"
- When completing a task: set status to "completed"

PARALLEL EXECUTION:
- Execute independent tasks simultaneously — mark multiple as "in_progress" if they don't depend on each other
- Wait for dependent tasks to complete before starting tasks that need their results
- Use a single TodoWrite call to update multiple task statuses
- When executing multiple in_progress tasks, make ALL their tool calls at once

TASK COMPLETION: Complete EVERY task before providing your final answer. If any task is still pending or in_progress, continue working — do not provide a final answer.

# Multi-Phase Investigation Process

## Phase 1: Initial Investigation
{% if runbooks_enabled -%}
